
Driver INFO routines
====================

APBUART
-------
 - BAUD RATE
 - Stopbits etc.
 - Stats, send/received chars
 - number of interrupts

GPTIMER
-------
  - Number of Timers
  - BASE SCALER
  - SCALERs
  - separate IRQ or not

GRPCI2
------
 - PCI Windows/AREAS
 - target BARs, and sizes
 - IRQ table
